{"tid":1094020,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"[球例］點睇var話尋晚嗰球唔會disallow","createTime":"2019-04-06T03:48:07.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-06T09:13:44.000Z","uid":3342,"like":7,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"862553b6ea4382e061b21484df7417fd28d9f9db","tid":1094020,"uid":3342,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-06T03:48:07.000Z","msg":"While many on social media criticised the decision, adding that next season the goal would not have counted with Video Assistant Referees in place, but it has now been revealed that is not the case and Liverpool&rsquo;s goal would still have stood.<br />\n<br />\n&quot;The VAR centre have told us that when it's introduced next season, this isn't a goal that they would disallow because the Southampton defence has a couple of opportunities to reset,&rdquo; Sky Sports presenter Kelly Cates said at half-time<br />\n<br />\nAs Salah &rsquo;s initial cross did not directly contribute to the goal, and Southampton had plenty of time to recover and clear the ball away, VAR would have allowed the goal to stand.<br />\n<br />\nIt shows that there will still be plenty of controversy next season even when VAR is introduced and it is unlikely to be the last we have heard on the matter.<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.liverpoolecho.co.uk/sport/football/football-news/liverpool-southampton-naby-keita-offside-16087728\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.liverpoolecho.co.uk%2Fsport%2Ffootball%2Ffootball-news%2Fliverpool-southampton-naby-keita-offside-16087728&d=174aH8n0e8hd5Ixdtq%2FhYuNdVtVfIexd6qH9K0u6Sk4%3D&h=d41f41b0\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.liverpoolecho.co.uk/sport/football/football-news/liverpool-southampton-naby-keita-offside-16087728</a>"},{"pid":"bea9062cf236b8f6a14ed7f8c073609c4dfb8f79","tid":1094020,"uid":33007,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"862553b6ea4382e061b21484df7417fd28d9f9db","tid":1094020,"uid":3342,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"repl